            . I was behind the coach; Keys came to me, and told me the handkerchief was taken - I went to the watch-house, and saw it - this is it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. Q. Had you seen me before? A. Yes - near Limehouse church.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence, I was not five minutes out of Whitechapel hospital; I had been knocked down and kicked by some young man, who broke open a house; I told them I had just got out of the hospital, and got up behind this coach; I saw another boy there - he dropped something, and the officer came and took me.</p>
